pages.text: About The Lounge at element, Downtown Sarasota's coolest bar and eatery.
Contact us at The Lounge at element

Book your next event with us!
Whatever the occasion, we will make sure your celebration is indelible. The Lounge is the perfect place with the perfect space for birthday parties, rehearsal dinners and any celebration in between.
Don’t let the time of day limit your experience. The Lounge is available for breakfast, brunch/lunch private events.
The Lounge capacities:
Up to 50 guests for a stand up mix & mingle
Up to 16 guests at one long table
